  "instructions": [
    "In a medium pot, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for one minute.",
    "Add the diced carrot, cumin, coriander, and bay leaf.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the red lentils, reduce heat, cover, and simmer for 20 to 25 minutes until the lentils are tender.",
    "Season with salt and stir in lemon juice for brightness.",
    "Serve hot, optionally topping with a drizzle of olive oil and fresh herbs."
